author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
The Heroes race deeper into the Jade Abbey's outskirts, catching a glimpse of their first big BOSS as he scurries deeper into the Mire. Foulhoof is ahead and Edmark leads his fellowship after the evil shaman to purge the Abbey of his curses!

Big thanks to GW for a complimentary copy of the box to review.
